| Document Type | Template |
|---------------|----------|
| Subsystem README | `_templates/subsystem-readme.md` |
| Detailed Component | `_templates/component-detail.md` |
| Guide/How-To | `_templates/guide.md` |
| ADR | `_templates/adr.md` |
| Composite Pattern | `_templates/composite-pattern.md` |
| Open Points | `_templates/open-points.md` |
| Operator Docs | `_templates/operator.md` |

